status_message:
Donald J. Trump: "I did not support the war in Iraq." 

FALSE. 

Trump was on the record as supportive of the Iraq War as early as a month before Congress voted to authorize military force in Iraq and even soon after the invasion. He didn't express his outright opposition to the war until more than a year later, in an August 2004 interview. http://cnn.it/2dv9Nuv #CNNRealityCheck
link_name: Reality Check: Trump and Iraq War
